casebody.data:
Prescilianq MARTINEZ and Madardo Abeyta v. J. Luis RIVERA. No. 2133. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth. Circuit. June 13, 1940. Robert H. LaFollette, of Albuquerque, N. M., for appellants. Gilbert & Hamilton, of Santa Fe, N. M., for appellee.

Before PHILLIPS and LEWIS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed, on motion of appellee at appellants’ costs, for failure to prosecute.
